              "type": "text",
              "content": "## Understanding Approximation Algorithms\n\nApproximation Algorithms explores the limits of computation and strategies for hard problems. This topic is essential for building a strong foundation in computer science and understanding how modern computing systems work from the ground up.\n\nComputer science is not just about programming — it's about understanding the principles of computation, information, and automated reasoning. Approximation Algorithms is a key piece of this larger puzzle."
